      <title>南非市场自 2022 年以来首次出现净外资流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/south-africa-posts-first-net-foreign-inflow-to-market-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在致力于促进经济增长的联合政府的推动下，南非报告称，其债务和股票市场自 2022 年以来首次出现外国投资者净流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/south-africa-posts-first-net-foreign-inflow-to-market-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 08:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长维勒鲁瓦表示，他认同市场对降息的看法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/ecb-s-villeroy-sees-more-cuts-before-rates-no-longer-restrictive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，欧洲央行将在 2025 年进一步降低借贷成本，而且在货币政策不再紧缩之前还有一段路要走。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/ecb-s-villeroy-sees-more-cuts-before-rates-no-longer-restrictive</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 07:57:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>齐姆巴：俄罗斯和伊朗专注于自己的战斗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-13/ziemba-russia-iran-concentrating-on-own-battles-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[叙利亚反对派领导的联盟在推翻总统巴沙尔·阿萨德后，准备组建过渡政府。据报道，阿萨德政权之所以如此迅速垮台，是因为缺乏盟友俄罗斯和伊朗的支持。但 Ziemba Insights 创始人 Rachel Ziemba 告诉彭博社《地平线》中东和非洲版主持人 Joumanna Bercetche，这两个国家都在忙于解决与以色列和乌克兰之间的问题。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-13/ziemba-russia-iran-concentrating-on-own-battles-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 07:55:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国经济第四季度初意外萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/uk-economy-unexpectedly-shrinks-at-start-of-fourth-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者准备迎接痛苦的预算，英国经济 10 月份连续第二个月萎缩，延续了首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的新工党政府令人失望的增长数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/uk-economy-unexpectedly-shrinks-at-start-of-fourth-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 07:05:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆勒称考虑到经济形势，欧洲央行利率仍处于高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/ecb-s-muller-says-europe-s-economic-recovery-expected-to-be-slow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员麦迪斯·穆勒表示，在经济增长疲软的背景下，欧洲央行的借贷成本可能过高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/ecb-s-muller-says-europe-s-economic-recovery-expected-to-be-slow</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 06:40:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼卢比突破 16,000 关口，采取“相当大胆”的干预措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/bank-indonesia-weilds-quite-bold-intervention-as-rupiah-falls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼表示，由于印尼盾兑美元汇率已跌破 16,000 这一关键心理关口，政府已积极干预市场以抑制其下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/bank-indonesia-weilds-quite-bold-intervention-as-rupiah-falls</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 04:42:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市三周跌幅最大，因经济中期选举缺乏惊喜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/chinese-stocks-fall-as-key-meeting-fails-to-deliver-surprise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管中国当局在重要政策会议上誓言要刺激消费，但政府再次让投资者猜测财政刺激措施的具体细节，导致中国股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/chinese-stocks-fall-as-key-meeting-fails-to-deliver-surprise</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 01:42:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>制裁前景抵消供应过剩影响，油价有望周线上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国可能对伊朗和俄罗斯实施更严厉的制裁，抵消了人们对明年全球石油供应大幅过剩的持续担忧，油价每周均上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Metinvest 因战乱暂停一半乌克兰煤炭产量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/ukrainian-steelmaker-halts-operation-at-coal-mine-in-donetsk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于顿涅茨克地区战火纷飞，乌克兰最大的钢铁制造商 Metinvest BV 暂停了一半的乌克兰煤炭生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/ukrainian-steelmaker-halts-operation-at-coal-mine-in-donetsk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 17:31:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国对冲基金创始人因涉嫌 13 亿美元税务诈骗在丹麦被判入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/british-hedge-fund-founder-sanjay-shah-jailed-over-cum-ex-scam-in-denmark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国对冲基金交易员桑杰·沙阿因策划了一起价值 10 亿美元的税务诈骗案被丹麦法官判处 12 年监禁，这是迄今为止欧洲庞大的 Cum-Ex 交易丑闻中判处的最重监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/british-hedge-fund-founder-sanjay-shah-jailed-over-cum-ex-scam-in-denmark</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 15:11:25 GMT</pubDate>
